It's about a half blind mom with his ungrateful son & no matter how he treated her, she will always pray, love, care  and treasure him. This is the second best telemovie i watched about "Mother's Love" after Janji Seorang Anak.

Chorus
I will return oh mother

my cheek when I meet you

How many nights did you stay up late
So that I could sleep to my content?
And how many times did you thirst

fearing that I may be in danger

and Oh what a harsh dawn that was

remember throughout my life

more tender towards you than mine"

no human being loves anything like it

• It's a weird day today. I feel sad, lonely & angry to myself. It's N birthday today and today is the first year i won't be with N to celebrate his birthday. After so many years of waking up in the morning knowing it's N birthday and thinking about his birthday dinner etc, i felt so sad and so down today. Harry said it's normal to feel that way since i've been with N for so long. Anyway, I emailed him to wish him well and to make myself better, i went to KLCC for Isetan Desserts Fair. Had healthy cupcakes & caramel banana crepe for lunch.
  • Went to Kirana to passed my invites to Shashue, Erry & Puan Kirana. They had an emergency alteration to do, so i helped them a bit :) Tedd is sick so he's not himself today. He's the clown for today :)
  • Had dinner at Ayam Penyet @ The Curve with Harry. It's not as nice as the one we had in Indonesia but it's good compared to other Ayam penyet that we tried around KL. I had the crispy ayam penyet today. and am soooooooooo full so had to cancel our plan of having Banana Royale. Btw, the Waroeng Ayam Penyet  serve Es Alpokat, Soda Gembira, Milo Dinosaur & Teh Sostro!!! I love Teh Botol Sostro :) I still remember that i used to buy lots of Teh Botol and Kotak Sostro when i was in Brisbane. There's one time that i really really obsessed with Teh Botol, I had to take a train to Brisbane Chinatown @ 5.30am to buy Teh Sostro because it's out of stock around Gold Coast. I reached The Valley and waited for the store to open and bought 5 dozens of them. Had to get them to delivered to my apartment @ Broadbeach and it can't even fit my fridge...hahaa those days...
  • I'll be in Singapore from the 16th - 19th. Will be buying lots of bioderma & magic liquid soap :) I'll be missing Harry so much.
My new watch from Betsey :) bought this last October but it reached my place last week :)
My grandma passed away today :( rip nenek!
